{"tid":576032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國童爬入藝術品拍照　港男勸止：爛晒喇！","createTime":"2018-02-28T14:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T01:44:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":219,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"1bfa9236b50f6aa76740cf52d63dd05d53f68fb3","tid":576032,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180228/photo/bkn-20180228144356572-0228_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180228161250\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180228%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180228144356572-0228_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180228161250&h=ea6a3665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n禍從「鯊魚」口出？近日Facebook專頁「影攝食」發貼，指有內地童無視圍欄，爬進一個以鯊魚為藍本的藝術品內，怒斥其行為損壞裝置！<br />\n<br />\n發貼者指事發於周二（27日）的中環香港海事博物館外。根據片段內容，有三名操普通話的女童，走入鯊魚藝術裝置的口內拍照，並不停踐踏鐵欄，鐵欄旁邊並貼有紙張，上面寫着「小心膠水」。<br />\n<br />\n拍攝者隨即以廣東話勸阻，不斷重覆指「有兩個嘢攔住咗你唔可以爬入去」，惟女童似乎不明所以，仍指向鯊魚稱「進裏面」。<br />\n<br />\n事後，疑似女童親人出面，以普通話稱「我聽不懂」，更指自己「我沒有要進去呀」，便匆匆拉走女童。拍攝者繼續理論：「大陸嚟唔係大晒呀」。最後女童家人再拋下一句「我聽不懂」，便離開現場。<br />\n<br />\n片段惹起網民兩極化留言，有人支持拍攝者行為，「起碼樓主會岀聲」、「如果再多一百幾廿萬個好始（似）你咁正直嘅人，香港會美好更多」；亦有人認為不應公審小朋友，「小妹妹是無辜的應該影大人」、「拍片放上網就覺得你好冇品囉」。<br />\n<br />\n該鯊魚裝置位於中環碼頭的香港海事博物館外，為展覽「鯊魚與人類」的戶外展品之一，原意是藉藝術品提高公眾對鯊魚保育的關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180228/photo/bkn-20180228144356572-0228_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180228161250\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180228%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180228144356572-0228_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180228161250&h=b2749f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180228/bkn-20180228144356572-0228_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180228%2Fbkn-20180228144356572-0228_00822_001.html&d=du0YLYPsBBuLhFdiObzj0DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=0ced87dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180228/bkn-20180228144356572-0228_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4c6ce158061cff6e24301ad2bce2f9742da2751e","tid":576032,"uid":22679,"like":234,"dislike":2,"score":232,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:37:07.000Z","msg":"衰種衰代"},{"pid":"defb94245bfaaecdb9f27c3533235d6cb8cba90f","tid":576032,"uid":8883,"like":721,"dislike":9,"score":712,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:37:46.000Z","msg":"亦有人認為不應公審小朋友，「小妹妹是無辜的應該影大人」<br />\n<br />\n呢個年紀仲話個細路無責任係侮辱緊佢而唔係保護佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796a9cbdb0c1f563daa15298e3b4b15a3c4fee0b","tid":576032,"uid":29314,"like":366,"dislike":3,"score":363,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"支那人最鐘意扮聽唔明。"},{"pid":"6b0d7cf8404662d5ef48c713ad0df04bcdc9e533","tid":576032,"uid":106326,"like":174,"dislike":2,"score":172,"quote":{"pid":"796a9cbdb0c1f563daa15298e3b4b15a3c4fee0b","tid":576032,"uid":29314,"like":366,"dislike":3,"score":363,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"支那人最鐘意扮聽唔明。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:40:46.000Z","msg":"昆蟲聽唔明人話好正常"},{"pid":"7a43888637dba3b1e7e593589f0130e903cf6cb7","tid":576032,"uid":110112,"like":201,"dislike":1,"score":200,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"死返大陸喇聽不懂<br />\n問有沒有打折嗰陣時又唔見你聽不懂"},{"pid":"d4fcf3ff76c1a90534634449d0a2541cef5b904c","tid":576032,"uid":15730,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"796a9cbdb0c1f563daa15298e3b4b15a3c4fee0b","tid":576032,"uid":29314,"like":366,"dislike":3,"score":363,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"支那人最鐘意扮聽唔明。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:45:16.000Z","msg":"唔知鬧佢支那人聽唔聽得明呢"},{"pid":"62cfe02b9cdd0a3fb6b99fb075d5aadde5997fc0","tid":576032,"uid":28913,"like":82,"dislike":1,"score":81,"quote":{"pid":"defb94245bfaaecdb9f27c3533235d6cb8cba90f","tid":576032,"uid":8883,"like":721,"dislike":9,"score":712,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:37:46.000Z","msg":"亦有人認為不應公審小朋友，「小妹妹是無辜的應該影大人」<br />\n<br />\n呢個年紀仲話個細路無責任係侮辱緊佢而唔係保護佢<img src=\"/a